	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have a question... why do the majority of my pets con green to me?  I'll get an occasional blue, but certainly never yellow.  I'm a Level 15 Dark Elf Necro and it's frustrating.<br><br>Any help or advice would be appreciated.  Thanx.<br><br>- Nefari<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
