	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>The strength of your pet may be determined in some way by your conjuration skill.  At the beginning of a level, I might summon low blue or green con pets, but after my conjuration skill has a chance to rise a little, I start casting more and more high blue con pets.  Just a thought<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
