	   <tr><td colspan=2>One thing that may be happening (this happened to me) is that you are summoning not the latest pet. Make sure that you are using convoke shadow. And also, just to clarify, the pet does not get weaker, it gets weaker in proportion to you<br><br><br>Winspus<br>Gnome with a tome!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
