	   <tr><td colspan=2>One more thing that matters is FRACTION! As a Iksar Necro fraction is VERY importen - thou will not help U level faster but can make youre life easier or vice a versa.<br><br>Another thing is how the hardness differs between same lvl mobs. Some mob flees earlier then others that may NEVER flee. If they mob up against U or how agro they are. If they are casters or have poison-/diseaseattacks. If they resist youre best DOT/DD spells etc etc.<br><br>There's alot of different aspect to WHERE to hunt and WHAT to hunt. Things that matter is WHAT class U are and what kind of abilities or spells you got. As an necro I have an overhand against undead critt thou to our powerfull spells reagarding undead.<br><br>Well there's my 2 coppers.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
