	   <tr><td colspan=2>One of the main reasons I choose to be an Erudite Necromancer, is that I do not always have a lot of time to devote to group play. While I do spend much of my time solo, occasional I have enough time where I can group for extend period of time.<br><br>While I have gotten pretty darned good at soloing, I would love to hear some stratiegies of fellow Necros in group play. What spells work the best, what niche do we fill, and how can we "wow" the group with our skills and tactics?<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
